body:
Age: 22
Amount of Games (ranked in s6) : 200    ...(yes i want to get out of this elo)
Main-Position: Supp>Jungle>Top>Mid>Adc
Elo: s5 for now (got hit by bronze drop)
TS: yes
TS-server: available
Skype: yes
Looking for a Team which should be at least silver. Pref gold from s5. Also this team should be competitive orientated.
My main Champs are for supp: Leona, Alistar, Soraka
For Jungle : Master Yi, Shyvana, Warwick
I am playing since Season 5 and got up to S1... with the Bronze drop i got thrown into B2 and do my best to reach my old goal to get into gold.(Right now im back to s4)
I can speak english,dutch and german so the communication with TS or Skype should not be a problem. (<--- very important!!!)

If you are interested please feel free to contact me in league.
IGN: Reanay

above is also the link for my lolking page. Hope to hear from some people.
Cya
